    "title": "Surpresssing Fires!!!",
    "description": "Always incendiary. Fires a main bullet; after ~0.15s it spawns three sideways-fanning bullets. After another ~0.15s, those bullets explode in a small radius for fire bullet damage. The main bullet has no splash."
  },
  "notes": "Uses the same skin as a purple Bandit rifle.\nSplit and detonation are flight time-based, not distance. Higher projectile speed pushes the explosions further out.\nSynergises with Make it Sparkle: Deathtrap only needs to be near the line of fire.\nThe first bullet has no splash. The three spawned bullets deal full gun damage and each adds a full splash detonation; if all connect this can reach up to 600% total shot damage. Grenade damage bonuses do not boost this splash.\nBoth bullets and explosions can ignite; if all parts hit, a shot has about a 31% chance to ignite.",
